---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 389
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=The Inner Pilgrimage
By: Sri Sankarâchârya
Commentary: \"Merging in Brahman, just as a man merges into water while
  bathing" (note by the translator, Swami Jagadânanda).
---
The mind is the place of pilgrimage where the devas, the Vedas and all
other purifying agencies become one. A bath in that place of
pilgrimage makes one immortal.
